Package: ok.gov
Title: State of Oklahoma Open Data CKAN Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the State of Oklahoma open data portal (CKAN API). Covers dataset search, metadata, datastore queries, and SQL access. Includes LLM context injection via ok_context().
